snippet.title: Unbox the Room Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/3017730/Unbox_the_Room/
Twitter: https://twitter.com/WeirdPenguinGms
Discord: https://discord.gg/ZC2qbGAEuU

Unbox the Room is a relaxing puzzle game where you unpack and arrange items and furniture in your new home. Create a cozy space by placing everything just right, from the smallest cup to the largest sofa.
